\SE[3]...Hey, Laura. It's great that you're so enthusiastic,
but how about taking a little break? \SE[1]Sure, I
appreciate that you're willing to do anything for me, but...

\SE[2]No, don't worry about it. \SE[5]I just can't seem to
calm down if I don't move my body a bit...

\SE[3]And also, you know... Since the environment has
changed a bit, I want to get used to it as soon as
possible... That's another reason. \SE[3]Oh, by the way...
What do you want to eat for tonight's dinner?

\SM[nod]\SE[13]Hmm...! Leave it to me...!! \SE[3]Then,
should I make it with spices! Vita seems to know a lot about
that kind of thing! \SE[1]I'll put my heart into making it,
so look forward to it...!

\SE[56]She's completely in a manic state, isn't she...
\!\SE[37]It might be unavoidable given the circumstances
with her having a strange goal.

\SE[51]Even though all I can do is wait for information...
\SE[36]If delicious curry rice is being made, \SE[37]I guess
that's fine... Hmm...

\SE[2]Oh, you have an unusual expression. Is there something
bothering you?

\SE[23]Ahaha... It's easy to see through, huh. But it's not
about me...

\SE[51]Even from my perspective, it's clear that she's
forcing herself... \!\SE[37]Is it really okay like this...

\SE[2]Well... isn't it fine? I think it's a good thing to
have a purpose in life. \SE[3]Even if that purpose is
something dark.

\SE[50]I've known that girl for a long time, but... \SE[3]In
her own clumsy way, she's the type who wholeheartedly faces
anything straightforwardly, right? \SE[50]On the other hand,
there was a part of her that couldn't establish a core.

\SE[74]If someone like that is focusing on one thing...
trying to live strongly... \SE[3]Then, isn't that fine?

\SE[12] (That's right... \SE[56] 'Onee-sama' is like a
'seeker of enlightenment' with a messed up mental
strength...)

\SM[double]\SE[16] Cat-chan News is here! \SE[0] We have
received some new information!

\SE[52]Ah... I'm sorry. \SE[37]It seems like it will take a
little more time for the witch part...
\SE[1]So, what is it? That new information you mentioned.

\SE[4]Th-this is also important information...! \SE[37]I was
asked to do it over 3 years ago, so it's quite late...!!
